{"tid":2492103,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"17元人仔海底撈食得飽？ 　網民分享超慳錢攻略","createTime":"2021-04-16T23:42:04.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-16T23:42:04.000Z","uid":271829,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"d0547a57a14a010c087ccfc9b9a142ed586e51dc","tid":2492103,"uid":271829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T23:42:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/Weq62ZjmMj1IzFcqTH3mJrw6LlY=/1920x1080/filters:quality(100)/d87urpdhi5rdo.cloudfront.net/04-16-2021/t_5309eda78e444a5d92a351f68a314d44_name_New_Project___2021_04_16T221422_158.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FWeq62ZjmMj1IzFcqTH3mJrw6LlY%3D%2F1920x1080%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fd87urpdhi5rdo.cloudfront.net%2F04-16-2021%2Ft_5309eda78e444a5d92a351f68a314d44_name_New_Project___2021_04_16T221422_158.jpg&h=1c8e1686&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n...<br />\n中國政府雖然宣佈國家全面脫貧，但人始終對慳錢和攞着數有所執着。近日內地有網民聲稱在知名連鎖火鍋店海底撈吃一餐只花了17元人民幣（下同，約20港元），實情只點一份撈面，其他食物都是店家免費提供。消息曝光後，其他網民爭相仿效效，有母親帶兩個兒童去海底撈消費，最終只花了27元（約32港元），亦有上海美食KOL利用海底撈免費提供的牛肉粒，在餐廳內煮出番茄牛肉等菜式。網民對此意見不一，當中更有人擔心海底撈遲早會加價。<br />\n<br />\n根據聲稱只花了17元吃海底撈的網民貼出的單據顯示，事主點了四份免費清水鍋，一份7元（約8港元）的撈麵，另外一份自選小料10元（約11港元），圖片顯示清水鍋中只有番茄、粟米等配料，事主還聲稱離開時帶走了不少花生、水果及牛肉粒，還順便做了手部護理，「吃的穩賺不賠」。<br />\n...<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20210417/M6US2JOGUNANZCB6FFDS4QKR4M/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20210417%2FM6US2JOGUNANZCB6FFDS4QKR4M%2F&d=8tl7d8txXkgslZB5fT8CLyL1bdbhbSvxCnYHZ8iA0HE%3D&h=fd9d4d8d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20210417%2FM6US2JOGUNANZCB6FFDS4QKR4M%2F&h=e33ed71f\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20210417/M6US2JOGUNANZCB6FFDS4QKR4M/</a>"}]}